"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-news-newslens-2024-0507-1447707-olympic-breakdancer\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Moonwalking into the centre of a colourful gladiator-like stage, South African breakdancer Courtnae Paul warms up a Johannesburg crowd with jazzy bobs and a contagious smile.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 116, \"end\": 128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannesburg\", \"score\": 0.9999999804485926, \"rank\": 1.9551612935583877e-08, \"text\": \"Johannesburg\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannesburg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannesburg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is competing in one of the last few events left before the sports' much-awaited Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the blink of an eye, she's upside-down propped up by one arm, her brown-blonde ponytail swaying behind her.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking, short for breakdancing, was added to the Paris 2024 Olympic roster after enjoying wide success at the Summer Youth Olympic Games in Buenos Aires in 2018.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 439, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.835063473764886e-21, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 530, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"score\": 0.9999999937322173, \"rank\": 3.5706157289263444e-09, \"text\": \"Buenos Aires\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a mixture of martial arts, gymnastics - all the cool stuff,\\\" Paul said of the sport.\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The dancer bagged her second career trophy at the prestigious Johannesburg tournament last month.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannesburg\", \"score\": 0.9999999804485926, \"rank\": 1.9551612935583877e-08, \"text\": \"Johannesburg\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannesburg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannesburg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Born in the coastal city of Durban, the 32-year-old is one of seven African break dancers - known as B-girls and B-boys -- vying to make it to Paris.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.487913837509593e-13, \"text\": \"Durban\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\"}, {\"begin\": 887, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.6598689716758174e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Along with a fellow South African B-girl, she is hoping to catch a break in upcoming qualifiers in Shanghai and Budapest.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"score\": 0.9999999987726369, \"rank\": 1.0789526964784319e-09, \"text\": \"Shanghai\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\"}, {\"begin\": 1007, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999831093193, \"rank\": 1.6885116829493167e-08, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paul said she got into breakdancing almost by chance, having previously practised gymnastics, kickboxing, Muay Thai and other sports.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1124, \"end\": 1133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kickboxing\", \"score\": 0.7547153317019676, \"rank\": 0.32500289578732017, \"text\": \"Muay Thai\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kickboxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kickboxing\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After moving to Johannesburg dreaming of a professional dancing career, she started working as a choreographer as well as backup dancer, DJ and media entrepreneur.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1316, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The decades-old street dance style always appealed to her but she practised mostly as a hobby, \\\"doing nonsense until it formed into something\\\" thinking nothing much would come out of it.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was nowhere for me to take it - no platforms existed,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1577, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then in 2020, the coronavirus pandemic hit with its lockdowns, giving Paul ample time to dedicate to her passion.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was God's way of saying: \\\"Let us get you back to the thing we want you to do,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd like to have been, you know, six years younger, but I will take what I can get.\\\"\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Explosive, powerful lady'She developed a unique style, which she describes as a mixture of her self-starter \\\"roughness\\\", \\\"education\\\" and \\\"South African flavour\\\".\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 2036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her trainer, Jaco Claasen, described her during a session as an \\\"explosive\\\" and \\\"powerful lady\\\" who literally throws herself into her moves.\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In preparation for the Olympics, he said much of the work will go to fine-tuning her stability and muscle connection to handle the force.\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Forty other female dancers from across the world are taking part in qualifiers this month and the next.\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Only 16 will go to Paris.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2443, \"end\": 2448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.6598689716758174e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There they will battle it out for gold through four one-on-one clashes or throwdowns, lasting up to 60 seconds.\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A DJ will choose the beat.\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2565, \"end\": 2567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999966198629, \"rank\": 2.598667267651329e-09, \"text\": \"DJ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their performance will be ranked based on criterias including technique, musicality and originality.\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paul said she was astounded when she learnt Paris was on the cards.\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2737, \"end\": 2742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.6598689716758174e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Breaking has been added as an official Olympic sport,\\\" she recalled a friend telling her.\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not believe it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But chasing her dream has not been easy as the nascent sport is yet to attract enough big sponsorships.\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nine out of 10 times, everything is coming out of my pocket,\\\" said Paul, adding she can compete in only a handful of events a year, lacking the money to travel more.\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In a perfect world, I'd be a professional athlete and get paid to train, eat and sleep, unfortunately in South Africa, that's not my reality.\\\"\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3259, \"end\": 3271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9998588234162706, \"rank\": 0.0001411840097221271, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic visibility is hopefully going to change that, making life easier for future athletes, she said.\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The circuits that have been built around Olympic qualifiers are game-changing,\\\" Paul said.\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have worked as hard as I can, and I am as ready as I can be.\", \"from\": 3496, \"to\": 3559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A self-assured person is a dangerous one!\\\"\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3602, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Source:AFP  \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3627, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 3628, \"to\": 3718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3653, \"end\": 3676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851270567, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 3678, \"end\": 3685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.999998996256685, \"rank\": 1.0006852813449238e-06, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9 is not responsible for the content of external internet sites.\", \"from\": 3719, \"to\": 3785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3719, \"end\": 3722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Images Courtesy of Getty Images.\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3806, \"end\": 3811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999842730039538, \"rank\": 8.635284170971157e-06, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}]}"